ZH: 这块木板裂开了。
EN: This wooden board has split.

ZH: 他的手掌裂开了一个大口子。
EN: His palm has a big cut on it.

ZH: 由于地震，地面裂开了。
EN: The ground cracked due to the earthquake.

ZH: 这本书的书脊裂开了。
EN: The spine of this book is split.

ZH: 她的嘴唇裂开了，可能需要缝合。
EN: Her lips split and may need stitches.

ZH: 那颗树的树干裂开了。
EN: The trunk of that tree has cracked.

ZH: 泥土在烈日的炙烤下裂开了。
EN: The soil cracked under the scorching sun.

ZH: 房屋墙壁由于装修不当，开始裂开了。
EN: The walls of the house started to crack due to poor renovation.

ZH: 这个陶瓷饭碗已经裂开了。
EN: This ceramic bowl has already cracked.

ZH: 他的心裂开了，因为他的恋人离开了他。
EN: His heart broke as his lover left him.

ZH: 水池的底部裂开了一个大裂缝。
EN: There is a big crack on the bottom of the pool.

ZH: 桌子的一角裂开了。
EN: One corner of the table has split.

ZH: 灾难过后，城市裂开了。
EN: The city split apart after the disaster.

ZH: 岩石尖刺从地面上冒出，使地面裂开了。
EN: Rock spikes emerged from the ground, splitting it apart.

ZH: 这个钢筋混凝土柱子开始裂开了。
EN: This reinforced concrete pillar has started to crack.

ZH: 她的声音仿佛从裂开的地狱中传出。
EN: Her voice seemed to come from the depths of a shattered hell.

ZH: 他的皮肤从寒冷的天气中裂开了。
EN: His skin split from the cold weather.

ZH: 雨水使山谷底部的土地裂开了。
EN: The rain caused the land at the bottom of the valley to split.

ZH: 这个花瓶被打破了，裂开的碎片散落一地。
EN: This vase is broken, and its shattered pieces are scattered everywhere.

ZH: 海浪冲击后，礁石裂开了。
EN: The rocks split apart after being hit by the waves.
